\v 9 and may be found in him, not having my righteousness \add which is\add* from the law, but \add which is\add* through faith in Christ,\f + \fr 3:9 \ft Or “through Christ’s faithfulness” \f* the righteousness from God on the basis of faith,\f + \fr 3:9 \ft Or “on the basis of \fq his \ft faithfulness” \f* 
