\v 12 I know \add how\add* both ⸤to make do with little⸥\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Literally “to be humbled” \f* and I know \add how\add* ⸤to have an abundance⸥\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Literally “to abound” \f*. In everything and in all \add things\add* I have learned the secret both to be filled and to be hungry, both ⸤to have an abundance⸥\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Literally “to abound” \f* and to go without. 
\v 13 I am able \add to do\add* all \add things\add* by the one who strengthens me. 
