\v 15 Now you also know, Philippians, that at the beginning of the gospel, when I departed from Macedonia, no church shared with me in the matter of giving and receiving except you alone, 
\v 16 because even in Thessalonica ⸤on more than one occasion⸥\f + \fr 4:16 \ft Literally “both once and twice” \f* you sent for my need. 
