\v 19 And my God will fulfill your every need according to his riches in glory in Christ Jesus. 
\v 20 Now to our God and Father \add be\add* the glory ⸤forever and ever⸥\f + \fr 4:20 \ft Literally “to the ages of the ages” \f*. Amen.
